DataElement.preferredDefinition: Numeric value to represent the volume of the prostate in cubic centimeters (cc) as calculated from the length, width, and height of the gland.

DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: The walnut shaped accessory sex gland of the male reproductive system. It is located in the pelvis just below the bladder, surrounding the prostatic part of the urethra.
